--==AutoViewer==--
Created by Dave Harold

--==About==--
This program will browse the selected urls in a minimized, invisible, Internet Explorer browser window. Each url will be opened up in its own tab. It will browse the 4 urls for 3 minutes, close, and start again using a different proxy, if you want to use a proxy.

--==Setup==--
1. Enter the desired urls into the input boxes,save the urls if you wish by clicking the corresponding button.
2. If you wish to use a proxy click on the proxy tab and check the box marked "Use Proxy?"
3. Add valid HTTP proxies using the format given (123.123.123.123:444), save the proxies if you wish by clicking the corresponding button.
   If you decide not to use proxies leave the "Use Proxy?" UNchecked.
4. Click "Start" to earn some cash. 
5. When you are done CHECK the box marked "Check to stop"
-NOTE-
Manually editing the ini file may cause problems, do so at your own risk.
